SELECT count(*) FROM deliverer as del
JOIN [order] as ord
ON ord.deliverer_id = del.id
JOIN order_details as ord_det
ON ord_det.order_id = ord.id
JOIN discount as dis
ON dis.id = ord.discount_id
OPTION(FORCE ORDER);
